# SDNC paper artifact outputs are regenerated on demand by
# scripts/paper/run_paper_suite.sh. They are not committed because:
#   - weights.qlmw is 10.6 MB (regenerated bit-identically from the ISA spec)
#   - the trace JSONLs are large (~MB each)
#   - the README's "Expected checksums" section is the canonical contract;
#     deviation between regenerated outputs and those checksums is the bug
#     signal, not the absence of the files themselves
outputs/
